sub_title: Business Development Manager | Project Manager | Stakeholder Manager | Account Manager
summary:
I have always enjoyed managing various programs and projects. I started with coordinating just one project and developed neccessary skills to manage a program with a set of 25 projects, involving international teams from 10 cross departments and an overall budget of EUR 70 mln. 

This has been a perfectly challenging and exciting journey for me. In my work, I have met with hundreds of people from commercial, government, NGOs, sports and arts sectors and learned from each of them. This has helped me with managing subordinate colleagues and a team of more than 80 partners.

I have been fortunate to meet with all those people and am very thankful for all their views and experiences that helped me grow personally and professionally, and I am open to new connections as there is still so much to learn there. 

Professional skills:
Project Management | Business Development | Strategic Planning |  Sales | Budget Management | People Management | Customer Support 

Personal interests:
Sports | Films | Music | Brain Games | International Relations | Tourism
